maxpower.statemachine.collections
Class SMStack

java.lang.Object
  com.maxeler.maxcompiler.v2.statemachine.StateMachineLib
      maxpower.statemachine.collections.SMStack

public class SMStack
extends com.maxeler.maxcompiler.v2.statemachine.StateMachineLib

An implementation of a stack for use within state machines, built upon SMArrayList. The top of the stack is at index 0. It is the responsibility of the user to ensure that only one method affecting state (push, pop, clear) is called on any given cycle. Otherwise, the resulting state will be inconsistent.
